history.proof: intros d a. induction a using mon_ind. - simpl. qsimpl time: 1 use: mult_mon_zero_r. - simpl. rewrite mult_mon_com. rewrite mult_mon_zero_r. qsimpl time: 1 use: mult_mon_zero_r.

exceptions.exn: In environment d, n : nat a : mon d IHa : mult_mon d (zero_mon d) a = a Unable to unify "mult_mon d (zero_mon d) a = a" with "c_n d n a = c_n d n a".

original: intros d a. induction a using mon_ind. - simpl. apply mult_mon_zero_r. - simpl. rewrite mult_mon_com. rewrite mult_mon_zero_r. apply IHa.
